  "summary": "This is a standard for generic name resolution with arbitrarily complex access control and resolution. It permits a contract that implements this EIP (referred to as a \"domain\" hereafter) to be addressable with a more human-friendly name, with a similar purpose to [ERC-137](./eip-137.md) (also known as \"ENS\").",
